led to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\\\"\"L9ECAV7KIM\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"262ff04b-8ba3-4a20-af0a-3be52f08b2ce\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"7956f9bc-8f3a-4ff1-9d2f-c7b3a04f2aa5\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-19T19:10:50.306344053Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,productcatalogservice,productcatalogservice-0,\"{\"\"message\"\":\"\"failed to query product by id: Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"warning\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-19T19:12:21.598301632Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,frontend-2,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to get product recommendations: failed to get recommended product info (#PHOTO202): rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"3ae26cd0-d7ee-49f7-a820-8d30000699a0\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"GET\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"59250000-36dd-4234-8408-a22462889279\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-19T19:22:12.08906251Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-1", "frontend-0", "frontend-2", "productcatalogservice-2", "productcatalogservice-1", "productcatalogservice-0"], "service_name": ["frontend", "productcatalogservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-01", "aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-08", "aiops-k8s-06"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault occurred from 2025-06-19T19:10:04Z to 2025-06-19T19:25:04Z. Please identify the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-19 19:10:04+00:00 to 2025-06-19 19:25:04+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "metric_analysis_findings": "从 Trace 数据中提取的信息，结合分析，我们可以评估 `productcatalogservice` 是否是故障的根因。以下是分析要点：\n\n### 异常指标\n我们观察到以下指标异常：\n- **`rrt`**（响应时间）: `productcatalogservice` 在所有 Pod 上均表现出显著增加。\n  - `productcatalogservice-1`: 响应时间从 7362.61 增加到 20129787.5（变化率约为 2.0）\n  - `productcatalogservice-2`: 响应时间从 6891.92 增加到 20132033.08（变化率约为 2.0）\n  - `productcatalogservice-0`: 响应时间从 1338.26 增加到 6711832.92（变化率约为 2.0）\n\n- **`failed_query_ops`**（失败查询操作）: `tidb-tidb` 的失败查询操作显著增加。\n  - 指标从 0.0 增加到 42.67（变化率约为 2.0）\n\n- **`duration_99th`**: TiDB 的响应时间显著增加。\n  - 从 0.01 增加到 64.85（变化率约为 2.0）\n\n### 假设验证\n根据数据:\n- `productcatalogservice` 的响应时间在所有 Pod 上均显著增加，与 TiDB 的数据库调用问题高度相关。\n- `tidb-tidb` 的失败查询操作和响应时间 (`duration_99th`) 增加，进一步支持 TiDB 的故障导致 `productcatalogservice` 的异常。\n\n### JSON 输出\n通过以上分析，我们支持初始假设，核心指标是 `productcatalogservice` 的 `rrt`，以及 `tidb-tidb` 的 `failed_query_ops` 和 `duration_99th` 的异常。因此，生成以下 JSON 输出：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt\", \"failed_query_ops\", \"duration_99th\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increased rrt across all pods due to TiDB's failed_query_ops and duration_99th issues, indicating region unavailability.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt increased almost 2x in productcatalogservice pods; failed_query_ops and duration_99th increased in tidb-tidb.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "log_analysis_findings": "从提取的日志中，我们重点分析了以下几点：\n\n### 分析结果\n1. **关键错误类型**: 发现多个服务（主要为 `frontend` 和 `productcatalogservice`）报告了 `Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable`。\n2. **日志频次和服务影响**:\n   - `productcatalogservice` 日志中的 \"failed to query product by id\" 错误频次较高（出现次数 148）。\n   - `frontend` 服务在尝试获取产品信息时的 `rpc error` 频繁，报告了类似的区域不可用错误。\n\n### 提取的关键字\n- `Error 9005 (HY000)`\n- `Region is unavailable`\n- `rpc error: code = Unknown desc`\n- `failed to query product by id`\n\n### 组件分析\n- **受影响的组件**: `productcatalogservice`\n- **抱怨的服务**: 大量日志显示 `frontend` 对 `productcatalogservice` 存在抱怨，且后者与 TiDB 进行操作时出现问题。\n\n这些数据进一步支持了初始假设：`productcatalogservice` 的确由于 TiDB 的区域不可用性引发的问题在本次故障中处于核心地位。\n\n### 结论\n根据日志分析，初始假设获得支持。因此：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"Error 9005\", \"Region is unavailable\", \"rpc error: code = Unknown desc\", \"failed to query product by id\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable leading to delays\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frequent 'failed to query product by id' logs with Error 9005 during the reported incident\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n这个结论符合所有服务和错误日志间的关联关系，明确表明 `productcatalogservice` 是本次故障的根因。"}
